Subscribe to the #SoundwithKlairs Youtube channel for more relaxing videos! ✨

A place to awaken your daily life🍵💚

Did you know that there’s a tearoom on the 2nd floor of @klairs.seoul?

As Klairs is a brand that aspires to become part of your daily lives, we thought about what we could do in order to provide a better experience for our customers. 

So @magpie.and.tiger and @klairs.seoul came together to open the 'Sinsa Tearoom', where our daily lives become more sensuous.

Feel the time going by slowly at Garosugil, the most busy and fast-paced place in Seoul.

Sinsa Tearoom will awaken your five senses and make you look back to the moments in your daily life that you might have overlooked.✨

Experience something new and make your daily life more colorful in this unusual space that may feel like a black, remote island.🙏🏻💕

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
From start to finish, A Moment is crafted solely by the artist’s hands. 

It takes dozens of meticulous steps for one objet to come to life. A rubber mold is cut, a metal casting is made, and finally, the objet is sanded multiple times for its smooth surface.

With the hope that A Moment will bring warmth to all your moments and new beginnings, may the subtle glimmer of platinum light up all parts of your day✨

[YYD Studio]
Seoul-based metal craftsman Yeo Dong Yun delivers joy through homeware and other items you can easily find in your daily life. @studio_yeodongyun
